<h1 class="h2">About Bet Management System</h1>

<p>
    Bet Management System is a fictional operations platform built for a betting account team that needs
    clean customer records, traceable account activity, and dependable balance management.
</p>

<p>
    The company was founded to replace spreadsheet-driven account tracking with a controlled web application.
    Administrators can manage customer profiles, create accounts after customers are registered, and keep a
    clear audit trail of debit and credit transactions.
</p>

<p>
    The application focuses on practical back-office workflows: search, validation, account status control,
    and role-based access for sensitive management pages.
</p>
